# 3-d charts better for if multiple columns also within same row , avoid labels if looking cluttered or messy
# remove duplicates option present in excel
# ctrl+H : find and replace only selected cells
# report connections option in slider tab : link elements as same (alias) in multiple sheets of same workbook


